    "sectionsText": "Key Learning Points ◆ @AbapCatalog.sqlViewName → Technical SQL view name visible in SE11 ◆ @AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter → Optimizes WHERE clause filtering ◆ @AbapCatalog.preserveKey → Preserves key fields as defined ◆ @AccessControl.authorizationCheck → #CHECK / #NOT_REQUIRED / #NOT_ALLOWED ◆ @EndUserText.label → Description text (SE11, ADT) ◆ @Environment.systemField:#CLIENT → Client field mapping for implicit WHERE ◆ @Semantics annotations → Define semantic meaning for fields ◆ define view { entity_name } → CDS entity name used in ABAP/openSQL | Concept Diagram CDS View Syntax — Key Elements @AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_SIMPLE' @AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK ── Annotations (metadata declarations) define view ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE ── View declaration (entity name) as select from /dmo/travel ── Source entity (CDS view or DB table) { key travel_id as TravelId, agency_id as AgencyId, customer_id as CustomerId, total_price as TotalPrice, currency_code as CurrencyCode, @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode' booking_fee as BookingFee } ── Element list with aliases key = primary key element ── Field-level annotations ANNOTATE DEFINE SELECT | CDS Source Code ",
